itter.com/SocialWinTW\" rel=\"SocialWinTW\" target=\"_blank\">@SocialWinTW</a></div>\r\n<a href=\"http://storify.com/SocialWinTW/aercomparte-ii-un-dia-lleno-de-social-media#50b6066876523f71072a60a1\" target=\"_self\">hace un día</a>\r\n<div><a title=\"Reply\" href=\"http://twitter.com/intent/tweet?in_reply_to=273382126689337344&amp;related=storify\">Reply</a><a title=\"Retweet\" href=\"http://twitter.com/intent/retweet?tweet_id=273382126689337344&amp;related=storify\">Retweet</a><a title=\"Favorite\" href=\"http://twitter.com/intent/favorite?tweet_id=273382126689337344&amp;related=storify\">Favorite</a></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>Un avance para que se vea que tuvo buenas recomendaciones:</div>\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img src=\"http://a0.twimg.com/profile_images/2369132556/no8bz7521blunp5f94nl_normal.jpeg\" alt=\"MarinaMldonado\" /></div>\r\n<div>3 C´s Comparte, Colabora y Comunica. <a title=\"Search for this hashtag on Twitter.com\" href=\"http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23AERCOmparte\" rel=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">#AERCOmparte</a><a title=\"sandopen on Twitter.com\" href=\"http://twitter.com/sandopen\" rel=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">@sandopen</a> No es época de uno solo, es época de compartir.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><a href=\"http://twitter.com/MarinaMldonado\" rel=\"MarinaMldonado\" target=\"_blank\">Marina Maldonado</a><a href=\"http://twitter.com/MarinaMldonado\" rel=\"MarinaMldonado\" target=\"_blank\">@MarinaMldonado</a></div>\r\n<a href=\"http://storify.com/SocialWinTW/aercomparte-ii-un-dia-lleno-de-social-media#50b6066876523f71072a60a5\" target=\"_self\">hace 20 horas</a>\r\n<div><a title=\"Reply\" href=\"http://twitter.com/intent/tweet?in_reply_to=273492054267543552&amp;related=storify\">Reply</a><a title=\"Retweet\" href=\"http://twitter.com/intent/retweet?tweet_id=273492054267543552&amp;related=storify\">Retweet<